Merlin's Bar & Grill, located at the base of Blackcomb Mountain, has a Canadiana log cabin feel and is known for apres ski boot dancing. The legendary Hairfarmers play live music from 3:45pm-6:45pm Monday, Wednesday and Friday during the winter season.
To avoid the on-mountain lineups, ski down to Merlin's for lunch.
Garibaldi Lift Co. (GLC), located at the base of Whistler Mountain, is a full service, elevated gastro pub experience including private firepits and signature cocktails.
To avoid the on-mountain lineups, ski down to the GLC for lunch.

Garbo's is a great way to start your day with Lavazza coffee and grab and go breakfast items. Or pop in at lunch for a mouth-watering burger!

To avoid the on-mountain lineups, ski down to the Dusty's for lunch.
